title: 1985 Hewlett-Packard Trophy
text:
The 1985 Hewlett-Packard Trophy was a women's <a href="tennis">tennis</a> tournament played on <a href="Tennis%20court">indoor carpet courts</a> in <a href="Hilversum">Hilversum</a>, Netherlands. It was part of the <a href="1985%20Virginia%20Slims%20World%20Championship%20Series">1985 Virginia Slims World Championship Series</a> and was played from 4 November until 10 November 1985. Unseeded <a href="Katerina%20Maleeva">Katerina Maleeva</a> won the singles title.
Finals.
Singles.
 <a href="Katerina%20Maleeva">Katerina Maleeva</a> defeated <a href="Carina%20Karlsson">Carina Karlsson</a> 6–3, 6–2
Doubles.
 <a href="Marcella%20Mesker">Marcella Mesker</a> / <a href="Catherine%20Tanvier">Catherine Tanvier</a> defeated <a href="Sandra%20Cecchini">Sandra Cecchini</a> / <a href="Sabrina%20Gole%C5%A1">Sabrina Goleš</a> 6–2, 6–2
